    <content type="html"><![CDATA[        <h1 id="my-blog"   >          <a href="#my-blog" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a><a href="#my-blog" class="headerlink" title="my blog"></a>my blog</h1>              <h3 id="1-安装Node-js"   >          <a href="#1-安装Node-js" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a><a href="#1-安装Node-js" class="headerlink" title="1.安装Node.js"></a>1.安装Node.js</h3>      <p>打开官网直接下载对应版本</p>        <h3 id="2-安装Git"   >          <a href="#2-安装Git" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a><a href="#2-安装Git" class="headerlink" title="2.安装Git"></a>2.安装Git</h3>      <p>打开官网直接下载对应版本</p><p>查看git是否安装成功</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#以管理员身份打开cmd</span><br><span class="line">git --version</span><br><span class="line">node -v</span><br><span class="line">npm -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>        <h3 id="3-安装Hexo"   >          <a href="#3-安装Hexo" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a><a href="#3-安装Hexo" class="headerlink" title="3.安装Hexo"></a>3.安装Hexo</h3>      <figure class="highlight plaintext"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g cnpm --registry=https://registry.npm.taobao.org #用淘宝的镜像源</span><br><span class="line">cnpm</span><br><span class="line">cnpm -v</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">cnpm install -g hexo-cli</span><br><span class="line">hexo -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>        <h3 id="4-新建文件夹"   >          <a href="#4-新建文件夹" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a><a href="#4-新建文件夹" class="headerlink" title="4.新建文件夹"></a>4.新建文件夹</h3>      <p>新建空文件夹（如blog）</p>        <h3 id="5-配置"   >          <a href="#5-配置" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a><a href="#5-配置" class="headerlink" title="5.配置"></a>5.配置</h3>      <p>在blog中打开git bash</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>        <h3 id="6-启动"   >          <a href="#6-启动" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a><a href="#6-启动" class="headerlink" title="6.启动"></a>6.启动</h3>      <figure class="highlight plaintext"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo s</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">hexo n &quot;filename&quot;</span><br><span class="line">#直接进到source中打开文件写博客</span><br><span class="line">hexo clean #清理</span><br><span class="line">hexo g #生成</span><br><span class="line">hexo s #启动</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>        <h3 id="7-部署在github"   >          <a href="#7-部署在github" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a><a href="#7-部署在github" class="headerlink" title="7.部署在github"></a>7.部署在github</h3>      <p>在blog文件夹中打开git bash</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cnpm install --save hexo-deployer-git #安装git插件</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure><p>打开github，注册</p><p>新建仓库</p><p>hxingjie  / hxingjie.github.io</p><p>在blog中打开git bash</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C &quot;your email@example.com&quot; #获取ssh密钥</span><br><span class="line">#多次回车</span><br><span class="line">出现The key fingerprint is: 和The key&#x27;s randomart image is:</span><br><span class="line">clip &lt; ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub #复制公钥</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure><p>登录github，打开settings，找到ssh and gpgp keys</p><p>创建新的ssh key</p><p>title中写任意文本</p><p>key中直接粘贴</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh -T git@github.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure><img src="C:\Users\何星杰\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20210511211649169.png" alt="image-20210511211649169" style="zoom: 67%;" /><p>配置git个人信息</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global user.name &quot;此处填你的用户名&quot;  </span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.email &quot;此处填你的邮箱&quot;</span><br><span class="line">#可用git config user.name，git config user.email查看用户名和邮箱</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure><p>打开github仓库</p><p><img src="C:\Users\何星杰\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\image-20210511211953665.png" alt="image-20210511211953665"></p><p>点击右上角绿色的code，找到ssh，复制</p><p>打开blog文件夹，找到_config.yml文件，打开，修改后如下</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># Deployment</span><br><span class="line">## Docs: https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment</span><br><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">    type: git</span><br><span class="line">    repository: git@github.com:hxingjie/hxingjie.github.io.git</span><br><span class="line">    branch: master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure><p>在blog文件夹中打开git bash</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line">hexo s</span><br><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure><p>之后写博客，只需</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo n &quot;blogname&quot;</span><br><span class="line">#打开source中的md文件写博客</span><br><span class="line">之后</span><br><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line">hexo s</span><br><span class="line">hexo d</span><br><span class="line">#还要打开github仓库，点开environments,hxingjie.github.io才会更新</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>        <h3 id="8-更新主题"   >          <a href="#8-更新主题" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a><a href="#8-更新主题" class="headerlink" title="8.更新主题"></a>8.更新主题</h3>      <p>例如：</p><p>打开<span class="exturl"><a class="exturl__link"   href="https://github.com/litten/hexo-theme-yilia" >https://github.com/litten/hexo-theme-yilia</a><span class="exturl__icon"><i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></span></span></p><p>复制地址</p><p>在blog/theme下打开git bash</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git clone git://github.com/litten/hexo-theme-yilia</span><br><span class="line">#完成后会在此文件夹下生成hexo-theme-yilia文件夹</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure><p>打开_config.yml文件，修改后如下</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># Extensions</span><br><span class="line">## Plugins: https://hexo.io/plugins/</span><br><span class="line">## Themes: https://hexo.io/themes/</span><br><span class="line">theme: hexo-theme-yilia</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure><p>再在blog下打开git bash</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line">hexo s</span><br><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>        <h3 id="9-主题显示错误解决办法"   >          <a href="#9-主题显示错误解决办法" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a><a href="#9-主题显示错误解决办法" class="headerlink" title="9.主题显示错误解决办法"></a>9.主题显示错误解决办法</h3>      <p>Hexo更改主题后启动服务器，界面显如下字符:</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">extends includes/layout.pug block content include includes/recent-posts.pug include includes/partial</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure><p>解决方案:</p><p>执行如下命令：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><div class="table-container"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install --save hexo-renderer-jade hexo-generator-feed hexo-generator-sitemap hexo-browsersync hexo-generator-archive</span><br><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line">hexo s</span><br><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>        <h1 id="引用"   >          <a href="#引用" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a><a href="#引用" class="headerlink" title="引用"></a>引用</h1>      <p>1.<span class="exturl"><a class="exturl__link"   href="https://blog.csdn.net/qq_36759224/article/details/82121420?ops_request_misc=%7B%22request_id%22:%22162070203316780269848986%22,%22scm%22:%2220140713.130102334.pc_all.%22%7D&amp;request_id=162070203316780269848986&amp;biz_id=0&amp;utm_medium=distribute.pc_search_result.none-task-blog-2~all~first_rank_v2~hot_rank-6-82121420.first_rank_v2_pc_rank_v29&amp;utm_term=%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2&amp;spm=1018.2226.3001.4187" >https://blog.csdn.net/qq_36759224/article/details/82121420?ops_request_misc=%7B%22request%5Fid%22%3A%22162070203316780269848986%22%2C%22scm%22%3A%2220140713.130102334.pc%5Fall.%22%7D&amp;request_id=162070203316780269848986&amp;biz_id=0&amp;utm_medium=distribute.pc_search_result.none-task-blog-2~all~first_rank_v2~hot_rank-6-82121420.first_rank_v2_pc_rank_v29&amp;utm_term=搭建博客&amp;spm=1018.2226.3001.4187</a><span class="exturl__icon"><i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></span></span></p><p>2.<span class="exturl"><a class="exturl__link"   href="https://www.jb51.net/softjc/715508.html" >https://www.jb51.net/softjc/715508.html</a><span class="exturl__icon"><i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></span></span></p><p>3.codesheep <span class="exturl"><a class="exturl__link"   href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Yb411a7ty?t=970" >https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Yb411a7ty?t=970</a><span class="exturl__icon"><i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></span></span></p><p>4.<span class="exturl"><a class="exturl__link"   href="https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_44318830/article/details/104884936" >https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_44318830/article/details/104884936</a><span class="exturl__icon"><i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></span></span></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
